data.title: Marines TV
data.meta_description: This edition features a story on Marines of Marine Medium Tiltrotor Squadron 162 performing daily maintenance ensuring operability of the Osprey helicopters. Hosted by Marine Sgt. Ricardo Gomez. Includes soundbites from Capt. Ray Scott, assistant operations officer, Marine Medium Tiltrotor Squadron 162.
data.text:
